under our system of proportional

20:54.553 --> 20:57.223 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
representation in the
Democratic Party.

20:57.223 --> 21:01.861 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, we're hoping early on to
demonstrate that Bernie Sanders
is the strongest candidate

21:01.861 --> 21:05.664 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
for the Democratic Party. We can
bring new people into the
process, young people
particularly,

21:05.664 --> 21:10.936 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
